dict_wrist = {'Brush_teeth':0, 'Climb_stairs':1, 'Comb_hair':2, 'Descend_stairs':3, 'Drink_glass':4,
              'Eat_meat':5,'Eat_soup':6,'Getup_bed':7,'Liedown_bed':8,'Pour_water':9,'Sitdown_chair':10,
              'Standup_chair':11,'Use_telephone':12,'Walk':13 }

def read_file(dict_wrist):
    '''
        Hm c file 
        -----------------
        Tham s:
            class_dict: mt dictionary cha 14 hnh ng c gn nhn t 0 n 13
        -----------------
        Tr v: 
            X: mt list c len = 14 cha d liu  c c (Mi phn t ca list c dng numpy array cha cc sample ca nhn )
    '''
    X = []
    for c in dict_wrist.keys():
        f = glob.glob(root + c + '/*')
        d = read_each_file(f, cls=c)
        X.append(d)
    return X #type list

def read_each_file(files, cls):
    temp = []
    for f in files:
        data = pd.read_table(f, sep=' ', header=None)
        data = np.array(data)
        temp.append(data)
    return temp

def prepare_data(data):
    '''
        Hm tch features v labels
        ---------------------------
        Tham s: 
            data: list cha cc d liu va c c
         ---------------------------------------------
        idx| size | value                            |
        ----------------------------------------------
        0  |  12  | (2167,3), (844,3), ...           |
        ----------------------------------------------
        1  | 102  | (270,3) , (270,3), ...           |
        ----------------------------------------------
        2  |  31  | ...                              |
        ----------------------------------------------
        3  |  42  | ...                              |
        ----------------------------------------------
        .  | ...  |
        .  | ...  | ...                              |
        .  | ...  |
        ----------------------------------------------
        13 | 100  | (1170,3), (956,3)                |
        ----------------------------------------------
        Tr v:
            X: list c chiu di l 839, tng ng 839 samples
            y: 839 labels
        ---------------------------------------------
        idx| size                                   |
        ----------------------------------------------
        0   |  (2167,3)                              |
        ----------------------------------------------
        1   |  (844,3)                               |
        ----------------------------------------------
        2   |  (2228,3)                              |
        ----------------------------------------------
        3   |                                        |
        ----------------------------------------------
        .   | ... 
        .   | ...                                    |
        .   | ... 
        ----------------------------------------------
        838 | (1050,3)                               |
        ----------------------------------------------
    '''
    X = []
    y = []
    for i,f in enumerate(data): #i chy t 0 n 13, f
        for ii in f:
            X.append(ii)
            y.append(i)
    return X, y

In [6]:
def extract_feature(X):
    '''
    Hm Trch chn c trng theo tiu ch mean, std, min, max.
    ---------------------------------
    Tham s:
        X: list c chiu di l 839, tng ng 839 samples
    ---------------------------------
    Tr v:
        temp: list c chiu di 839, mi phn t l mt numpy array c shape l (1,12)
    '''
    temp = []
    for arr in X:
        a = (np.mean(arr,axis =0)).reshape(1,3)
        b = (np.std(arr,axis =0)).reshape(1,3)
        c = (np.max(arr,axis =0)).reshape(1,3)
        d = (np.min(arr,axis =0)).reshape(1,3)
        temp.append(np.concatenate((a, b, c, d), axis=1))
    return temp

def vectorization(X):
    '''
    Hm Chuyn tng sample thnh vector (12,) chiu
    ---------------------------------------------------
    Tham s:
        X: list c chiu di 839, mi phn t l mt nummpy array c dng (1,12)
        ----------------------
        idx |   size(1,12) |
        ----------------------
        0   |  (1,12)      |
        ----------------------
        1   |  (1,12)      |
        ----------------------
        2   |  (1,12)      |
        ----------------------
        3   | ...          |
        ----------------------
        .   | ...          |
        .   | ...          |
        ----------------------
        838 |  (1,12)      |
        ------------------------------------------------
    Tr v:
        X: list c chiu di 839, mi phn t l mt nummpy array c dng (12,)
        ----------------------
        idx |   size(12,) |
        ----------------------
        0   |  (12,)      |
        ----------------------
        1   |  (12,)      |
        ----------------------
        2   |  (12,)      |
        ----------------------
        3   | ...         |
        ----------------------
        .   | ...         |
        .   | ...         |
        ----------------------
        838 |  (12,)      |
        ----------------------
    '''
    for i in range(len(X)):
        X[i] = X[i].flatten()
    return X

S khc nhau gia cc matric:

  • accuracy_score:

    Trong bi ton phn loi a nhn, hm ny tnh ton chnh xc ca tp hp con: tp hp nhn c d on cho mt mu phi khp chnh xc vi tp nhn tng ng trong y_true.

  • rand_score:

    Ch s Rand tnh ton o tng t gia hai cm bng cch xem xt tt c cc cp mu v m cc cp c ch nh trong cc cm ging nhau hoc khc nhau trong cm c d on v ng.

    The raw RI score is:

    RI = (number of agreeing pairs) / (number of pairs)

  • silhouette_score:

    H s Silhouette c tnh bng cch s dng khong cch trung bnh trong cm ( a) v khong cch trung bnh trong cm gn nht ( b) cho mi mu.

    Gi tr tt nht l 1 v gi tr km nht l -1. Cc gi tr gn 0 cho bit cc cm chng cho. Cc gi tr m thng ch ra rng mt mu c ch nh sai cm, v mt cm khc ging nhau hn.

Nhn xt:

Qua Kmeans phn cm dng c trng thng k dng bng v kim tra vi cc o khc nhau chng ta thy:

  • accuracy_score cho kt qu khng tt (0.103695) trn min accuracy [0,1]. iu ny cho thy c trng thng k dng bng c rt trch khng tt cho kha cnh phn lp.
  • rand_score biu din s khong cch gia cc cm. Khong cch cng xa th rand_score cng nh v khi rand_score nh th kt qu phn cm mi tt. Tuy nhin, vi c trng thng k, rand_score li cho kt qu ngc li (0.872220), iu ny cho thy cc cm phn c bng c trng thng k l gn nhau v khng tt cho qu trnh phn cm.

  • silhouette_score c min gi tr l [-1,1], biu din kh nng 1 im d liu c c phn cm ng hay khng. Vi c trng thng k, kt qu thu c l (0.251157). tt vi kha cnh phn cm im d liu l mc trung bnh.

  • Kt lun: kt qu tnh ton phn cm dng c trng thng k cho kt qu km 2 trn 3 o. iu ny cho thy c trng thng k khng tt vi bi ton phn cm vi d liu dng chui.

def data_visualization(X,y_pred):
    markers = ["s","o","d","v","*","^","h","x","+",".","4","D","|","<"]
    plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
    for ii in range(14):
        plt.scatter(X[:,0][y_pred==ii], X[:,1][y_pred==ii],cmap='Set2',marker=markers[ii],s=50)

Dimensionality reduction using Autoencoder¶

In [103]:
class AE(nn.Module):
  def __init__(self, **kwargs):
    super(AE, self).__init__()
    self.input_shape, self.encoder_shape = kwargs['input_shape'], kwargs['encoder_shape']

    # Encoder
    self.encoder = nn.Sequential(
      nn.Linear(self.input_shape, self.encoder_shape),
      nn.ReLU()
    )

    # Decoder
    self.decoder = nn.Sequential(
      nn.Linear(self.encoder_shape, self.input_shape)
    )
        
  def forward(self, X):
    encoded=self.encoder(X)
    decoded=self.decoder(encoded)
    return decoded

def train(model, error, optimizer, n_epochs, x):
    model.train()
    for epoch in range(1, n_epochs + 1):
        optimizer.zero_grad()
        output = model(x)
        loss = error(output, x)
        loss.backward()
        optimizer.step()

        if epoch % int(0.1*n_epochs) == 0:
            print(f'epoch {epoch} \t Loss: {loss.item()}')

device = torch.device("cuda" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu")

time_start = time.time()

model = AE(input_shape=wrist_X.shape[1], encoder_shape=3).double().to(device)
error = nn.MSELoss()
optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=1e-3, weight_decay=1e-3)

X_ae = torch.from_numpy(wrist_X).double().to(device)
train(model, error, optimizer, 1000, X_ae)

with torch.no_grad():
    encoded = model.encoder(X_ae)
    decoded = model.decoder(encoded)
    mse = error(decoded, X_ae).item()
    enc = encoded.cpu().detach().numpy()
    dec = decoded.cpu().detach().numpy()

time_ec = time.time() - time_start
print('ICA done! Time elapsed: {} seconds'.format(time_ec))

Tng kt

  • c trng PCA cho kt qu tt hn baseline tt c cc o. iu ny cho thy PCA thnh cng trong vic rt trch cc c trng phn bit ca d liu thng k, gip lm gim nhiu, loi b phn thng tin khng cn thit.
  • c trng t-SNE cho kt qu ch tt hn baseline o sihouette_score nhng li km hn hai o cn li. iu ny cho thy t-SNE gy nhiu mt mt thng tin khng cn thit v lm gim phn bit cm. Ngoi ra tc x l rt trch t-SNE lu hn cc phng php khc rt nhiu ln, cho thy km hiu qu ca t-SNE.
  • c trng KPCA cho kt qu tt hn so vi PCA( tt hn 2 trn 3 c trng), thi gian x l ca KPCA c phn lu hn PCA. iu ny cho thy c trng thng k cha thng tin phi tuyn v KPCA thnh cng rt trch c thng tin ny.
  • c trng ICA cho kt qu tt hn baseline tt c o. Tt hn PCA nhng km hn KPCA mt cht. iu ny cho thy ICA kh ph hp rt trch tng quan thng k trong c trng thng k, gp phn nng cao hiu qu phn cm ca Kmeans.
  • c trng autoencoder cho kt qu cao hn cc c trng khc trn 2 o sihouette_score v rand_score, iu ny cho thy kh nng tch bt cm ca Kmeans clustering trn c trng autoencoder l tt nht hin ti. Tuy nhin, kt qu accuracy biu th cho tt ca vic phn lp th autoencoder li rt km. Ngoi ra, tc x l ca autoencoder cng lu hn so vi PCA, KPCA, v ICA.

Nhn xt chung: c trng KPCA cho kt qu vt tri trn accuracy_score, ng thi kt qu trn hai o cn li cng mc tt. Thi gian x l ca KPCA cng c phn lu hn PCA v ICA, tuy nhin trade-off ny l ng b ra nh i vi hiu qu phng php ang li. So v cc tiu ch trn vi 4 phng php gim chiu d liu cn li, KPCA l phng php cho kt qu cao nht v tc x l n nh, ph hp cho x l c trng thng k.
